virginia 
florida is leading in many aspects of the competition 
skinner said the state that provides the money and effort to make 
this work will get the most government support 
a spaceport florida study says that a facility for launching 
small rockets that carry instruments to take various scientific 
soundings should be built at cape san blas near port st joe in the 
panhandles gulf county it also recommends two potential sites near 
the kennedy space center cape canaveral air force station using 
three inactive launch pads once used for atlas and titan missiles 
and the abandoned town of shiloh 
martinez said he is directing the florida department of commerce 
to take steps to develop the facility at cape san blas and to 
determine which of the two sites near the kennedy space center would 
be best for launching large payloads into orbit 
