about 200000 and could be open in nine to 12 weeks the air force 
once launched sounding rockets and many facilities are still 
available 
according to the study development of an orbital launch 
facilities on the east coast would require about three years 
ralph christi project leader for united engineers and 
construction the consultant that did the study for the state said 
a spaceport could be funded like an airport through revenue bonds 
or corporate debt 
