the pen of some ghost writer it comes from the heart 
brown installed last friday said the next time the 
administration says we need leadership thats kinder and gentler 
im going to ask kinder and gentler than whom the republican 
party 
in 1992 chimed in willie brown speaker of the california house 
we will capture the white house and give this nation a kinder and 
gentler leader 
that crop of ks and gs represents only the tip of the cliche it 
covers usage by a handful of political spokesmen since last 
thursday a check of associated press files turned up 140 stories 
using the phrase since the nov 8 election 
it has become fodder for tv comics promising kinder and gentler 
oneliners on groundhog day forecasts were for another six weeks 
of a kinder and gentler winter 
bush used his own line repeatedly during the presidential 
campaign startling his strategists one night when he said hed be 
kinder and gentler and would stop negative campaigning against gov 
michael dukakis by morning he had decided otherwise 
in conversation trying to remember a mans name bush described 
him as a kinder and gentler looking fellow 
in the inaugural address he declared a mission to make kinder 
the face of the nation and gentler the face of the world 
all of this flowed from a passage in his acceptance speech last 
aug 18 at the republican national convention crafted by campaign 
speechwriter peggy noonan who should have signed up for royalties 
on use of the line 
the fact is prosperity has a purpose bush said it is to 
allow us to pursue the better angels to give us time to think and 
grow prosperity with a purpose means taking your idealism and 
making it concrete by certain acts of goodness it means helping a 
child from an unhappy home learn how to read it means teaching 
troubled children through your presence that theres such a thing as 
reliable love some would say its soft and insufficiently tough to 
care about these things but where is it written that we must act as 
if we do not care as if we are not moved 
well i am moved he said i want a kinder gentler nation 
thats the line that stuck outlasting the cryptic thousand 
points of light turned on in the same speech 
but after six months it might be kinder and gentler to dream up 
a new catch phrase 
