<TEXT>
when the brothers appeared in hollywood movies in the 40s 
choreographer nick castle thought up mad tricks for the pair to 
do harold said nick castle jr wrote and directed tap 
most of the tappers had to take other jobs during the lean years 
said henry le tang 73 who choreographed tap and most of 
black and blue honi coles weathered those years working at the 
apollo theater harold nicholas spent the 50s working in europe le 
tang who always loved to teach opened a tap school when he was 20 
